{
    "_id": "tvHevcQsvCq20",
    "name": "TV HEVC QSV CQ20",
    "description": "H.264 (and legacy) TV -> HEVC via Intel QSV, quality 20, while ensuring a default English/undefined AAC stereo compatibility track. Skips HEVC and <6Mbps video encoding, but still remuxes missing/default AAC stereo with a 95-125% size guard. Drops fre/fra audio tracks, but only when a non-French audio track exists.",
    "tags": "",
    "flowPlugins": [
